### Başarılı senaryo — tüm adımlar geçer
POST http://localhost:5155/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Ahmet Yılmaz",
  "totalAmount": 299.99,
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 2
}

### Stok yetersiz — ProductId=999 → StockReservationFailed → OrderCancelled
POST http://localhost:5155/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Mehmet Kaya",
  "totalAmount": 149.99,
  "productId": 999,
  "quantity": 1
}

### Ödeme başarısız — Amount>1000 → PaymentFailed → ReleaseStock → OrderCancelled
POST http://localhost:5155/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Ayşe Demir",
  "totalAmount": 1500.00,
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 1
}